Singapore oil companies can set theirown petrol and diesel prices at the pump from today subject toceilings determined by their individual wholesale prices, TheMinistry of Trade and Industry said.    The ministry previously revised pump prices and announcedthe changes for the oil companies.    Lead content of petrol is further cut to 0.15 gm/litre from0.4 gm from today. Pump prices of the lower lead petrol gradesare expected to be announced soon by the oil companies whichhave said wholesale prices are between 1.3 cents/litre to 3.2cents higher than previous grades. REUTER&#3;